WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:02.040
Barclays Online Banking

2
00:00:02.640 --> 00:00:05.560
How to log in with your passcode
and memorable word

3
00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.080
Logging into Online Banking
is quick and easy.

4
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:14.800
Go to Barclays.co.uk
and click ‘Log in’ to begin.

5
00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:18.760
Next, type in your surname as
it appears on your account.

6
00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.320
Select one of the options,
then type in your details.

7
00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:25.880
Next, click ‘Continue’.

8
00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:28.760
You might then see this screen,

9
00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:31.840
which explains the limited
services available

10
00:00:31.840 --> 00:00:35.120
when logging in using a
passcode and card details.

11
00:00:35.240 --> 00:00:38.520
Scroll to the bottom and click
'Log in with passcode'

12
00:00:39.040 --> 00:00:40.520
Type in your passcode.

13
00:00:42.700 --> 00:00:45.440
Enter the requested characters of
your memorable word,

14
00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.000
before clicking on ‘Log in
to Online Banking’.

15
00:00:49.180 --> 00:00:52.040
And you’re now logged in.

